title: 158. Excellence: The Anti-Narrative
itunes:title: 158. Excellence: The Anti-Narrative
description: The stronger you are physically and mentally, the harder you are to be controlled. In today's episode, Andy talks about how we've been fed a narrative of division, what the possibilities are for people who are passive about what's happening in the world according to history, and why we need to come together in the name of freedom.
